{"id":519,"date":"2025-02-01T12:14:28","date_gmt":"2025-02-01T12:14:28","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/?p=519"},"modified":"2025-03-06T18:59:38","modified_gmt":"2025-03-06T18:59:38","slug":"vj-system-for-sazareba005","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/en\/vj-system-for-sazareba005\/","title":{"rendered":"VJ system for Sazareba#005"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"taxonomy-category wp-block-post-terms\"><a href=\"https:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/en\/category\/2024-02\/\" rel=\"tag\">2024.02<\/a><span class=\"wp-block-post-terms__separator\">, <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/en\/category\/personal\/\" rel=\"tag\">Personal<\/a><span class=\"wp-block-post-terms__separator\">, <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/en\/category\/touchdesigner\/\" rel=\"tag\">TouchDesigner<\/a><span class=\"wp-block-post-terms__separator\">, <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/en\/category\/unrealengine\/\" rel=\"tag\">UnrealEngine<\/a><span class=\"wp-block-post-terms__separator\">, <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/en\/category\/vj-en\/\" rel=\"tag\">VJ<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"ast-oembed-container \" style=\"height: 100%;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Sazareba 005 Archive\uff08i.s.d x RustyHead\uff09\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/4sW_tpFNxhk?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is a VJ system developed for an audio-visual performance at Sazareba #005. All effects are implemented in UE5 and rendered in real-time to produce interactive visuals synchronized with the audio. Specifically, TouchDesigner is used to receive and analyze audio signals in real-time, then transmit the audio data to UE5 via the OSC protocol. In UE5, the system is primarily divided into a camera controller and a VFX controller, both of which have their parameters controlled by a MIDI controller via the MIDI protocol.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Visual\uff1aRustyHead\uff08TAN YANGGU\uff09<br>Music\uff1ai.s.d\uff08Yuki Ishida\uff09<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" src=\"http:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/sazareba_03.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-528\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" src=\"http:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/sazareba_01.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-526\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" src=\"http:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/sazareba_02.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-527\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" src=\"http:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Untitled11.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-524\"\/><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This is a VJ system developed for an audio-visual performance at Sazareba #005. All effects are implemented in UE5 and [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":522,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"","ast-site-content-layout":"","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-t